    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 無調性打擊樂器操作<br>2. 有調性打擊樂器操作<br>3. 器樂合奏與編創<br>4. 打擊樂器於幼兒教學之應用<br>5. 幼兒表演活動設計<br>6. 創意敲打秀<br>",
        "en": "1. Atonal percussion <br>2. Tonal percussion <br>3. IEnsemble and Arrangement<br>4. The application of percussion instruments in early childhood teaching<br>5. Design of children's performance activities<br>6. Creative percussion<br>"
